name: Citrus Tale
description:
The head is the most beautiful madhouse. It has power to rationalise wound in the heart, make it more acceptable. The heart is the biggest misery castle. When the heart must swing, the mind we must step. The complex relationship between those two is the most admirable. - Elsadiora & Gun 2O Oct 2021
